WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:01.840
Huo Jiuling,

2
00:00:02.180 --> 00:00:05.200
I'm hurt. You're injured too; this isn't a good time for this.

3
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:05.800
It's not appropriate

4
00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:06.820
to do this right now.

5
00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.020
Are you concerned about me?

6
00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:15.000
Huo Jiuling...

7
00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:18.400
Don't move. We're on the third floor;

8
00:00:18.540 --> 00:00:20.340
a fall could be fatal.

9
00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:21.280
What do you intend to do?

10
00:00:21.760 --> 00:00:23.640
Kiss me.  I'll see you

11
00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:26.760
later. Is kissing me really so hard?

12
00:00:35.420 --> 00:00:36.820
You've only been here a short while,

13
00:00:36.820 --> 00:00:38.880
and you've already caused trouble.  We have

14
00:00:38.880 --> 00:00:40.000
many more days ahead,

15
00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:41.100
what are we going to do?

16
00:00:43.980 --> 00:00:44.660
Ji Lingling,

17
00:00:45.220 --> 00:00:47.160
Don't cry.  Stay with me,

18
00:00:47.300 --> 00:00:49.880
and we'll do all the things couples do together.

19
00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:50.800
Don't worry,

20
00:00:50.980 --> 00:00:52.940
don't be scared, okay?

